{"tid":1029272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李銳今出殯 高瑜浦志強被禁出席","createTime":"2019-02-20T06:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T04:02:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d48d7cf95f726507e9006a3042f2b84112d4e1a1","tid":1029272,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:24:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190220/20616587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F20616587&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8y3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=c5893f1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F20616587&h=5ef85e03\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190220/20616587</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李銳今出殯 高瑜浦志強被禁出席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190220/large/a1406a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190220%2Flarge%2Fa1406a.gif&h=273ec917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李銳家中擺滿花圈。<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東前秘書、中共「自由派」元老李銳16日在北京去世，終年101歲。李銳的告別式今早在北京八寶山公墓舉行。李銳生前好友、中國獨立記者高瑜透露，她和中國維權律師浦志強均接到通知，不准去李家弔唁，也不能參加喪禮。高瑜在Twitter稱：「為阻止我到李銳先生家弔唁，阻止我周三到八寶山再見李銳老最後一面，中午國保和警察就到我家，告訴我開始24小時上崗（限制自由） 。」她除了24小時被監視外，出門需要坐警車。高瑜又稱浦志強也接到禁止弔唁的通知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n友人拒參與官方葬禮<br />\n<br />\n由於李銳生前的敢言，中共對他的逝世十分低調，但有消息稱中組部給李銳的生平對其有相當高的評價，他去世後是中組部老幹部局副局長帶兩個處長去李家談善後。官方將按照正部級規格舉行葬禮，具體安排是8時30分首長悼念，9時以後開放給群眾悼念。目前知道送別幹部至少是政治局委員級別，尚不清楚會否有常委級別出席。<br />\n<br />\n由於李銳生前曾有「不開追悼會，不進八寶山，不蓋黨旗」的遺言，故也有李銳的友人決定不出席由官方組織的葬禮。前中組部幹部、《進出中組部》作者閻淮稱自己因親耳聽到李銳的「三不」遺言，出於對老人家的尊重，故而決定不出席相關儀式性活動。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n中國黑客恢復攻擊美企<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n4,370萬次下載擊敗抖音微信 學「習」App阿里開發"},{"pid":"93c95bb1f498974cb299b4673b6c9743a31eb370","tid":1029272,"uid":187858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"做共產黨都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死左都要比人當公仔咁舞<br />\n<br />\n又分先後又分級數<br />\n死左都不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下世投胎投好d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5c7ffd9cc5c60aebddf384d9f45d7207f827bf","tid":1029272,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93c95bb1f498974cb299b4673b6c9743a31eb370","tid":1029272,"uid":187858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"做共產黨都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死左都要比人當公仔咁舞<br />\n<br />\n又分先後又分級數<br />\n死左都不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下世投胎投好d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T17:21:52.000Z","msg":"蒙毛寵召啦仲投乜胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773d05d8415e218f6364402697c3e23cb38d3a63","tid":1029272,"uid":133519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca5c7ffd9cc5c60aebddf384d9f45d7207f827bf","tid":1029272,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93c95bb1f498974cb299b4673b6c9743a31eb370","tid":1029272,"uid":187858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"做共產黨都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死左都要比人當公仔咁舞<br />\n<br />\n又分先後又分級數<br />\n死左都不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"